messages.content: ComfyUI-path-util is a path utility for ComfyUI.
What is the purpose of ComfyUI-path-util?
The purpose of ComfyUI-path-util is to provide path-related functionality for ComfyUI.
No, ComfyUI-path-util is not a standalone application. It is a utility specifically designed for use with ComfyUI.
Does ComfyUI-path-util work independently of ComfyUI?
No, ComfyUI-path-util is meant to be used within the ComfyUI environment to assist with path-related tasks.
